        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、表单"><a href="#一、表单" class="headerlink" title="一、表单"></a>一、表单</h2><ul><li><p>提交方式：【get，post】</p><ul><li>最直观的区别就是GET把参数包含在URL中，POST通过request body传递参数。</li><li>GET不安全，相较而言POST安全一点</li></ul></li><li><p>形式：</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">form</span> <span class="attr">action</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">First name: <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;firstname&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">Last name: <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;lastname&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>表单标签汇总</p><p>- </p><ul><li><table><thead><tr><th align="center">标签</th><th align="left">描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center"><form></form></td><td align="left">定义供用户输入的表单</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><input></td><td align="left">定义输入域</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><textarea></textarea></td><td align="left">定义文本域 (一个多行的输入控件)</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><label></label></td><td align="left">定义了 <input> 元素的标签，一般为输入标题</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><fieldstet></fieldstet></td><td align="left">定义了一组相关的表单元素，并使用外框包含起来,说明语义，更加友好</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><legend></legend></td><td align="left">定义了 <fieldset> 元素的标题</fieldset></td></tr><tr><td align="center"><select></select></td><td align="left">定义了下拉选项列表</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><opgroup></opgroup></td><td align="left">定义选项组</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><option></option></td><td align="left">定义下拉列表中的选项</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><button></button></td><td align="left">定义一个点击按钮</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><datalist><strong>New</strong></datalist></td><td align="left">指定一个预先定义的输入控件选项列表</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><keygen><strong>New</strong></td><td align="left">定义了表单的密钥对生成器字段</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><output><strong>New</strong></output></td><td align="left">定义一个计算结果</td></tr></tbody></table></li></ul></li><li><p>表单标签使用案例</p><ul><li><pre><code class="html">&lt;body&gt;    &lt;h1&gt;表单标签使用案例&lt;/h1&gt;    &lt;p&gt;这部分内容分两个部分介绍&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ol&gt;        &lt;li&gt;1.  基本标签&lt;/li&gt;        &lt;li&gt;2. 表单和服务器的交互（Python Flask 构建框架）&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;/ol&gt;        &lt;p&gt;        表单是接受用户输入，然后将输入传递给服务器，然后服务器根据用户的需求产生个性化输入的控件。    &lt;/p&gt;    &lt;h2&gt;表单控件的使用&lt;/h2&gt;    &lt;!-- 基本结构 form开始和结束标签  --&gt;    &lt;!-- action指定数据交给服务器中那个程序处理 --&gt;    &lt;!-- method规定使用什么方法传递数据：get  or post --&gt;    &lt;!-- autocomplete 用于启用自动填充 --&gt;    &lt;form action=&quot;&quot; method=&quot;&quot; autocomplete=&quot;on or off&quot;&gt;        &lt;!-- input插件用于接受用户的输入，包含了多种输入插件 --&gt;        &lt;!--  name=&quot;必须&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; size=&quot;数字&quot; placeholder=&quot;提示信息&quot; --&gt;        &lt;!-- 关于label 要明白for的作用 --&gt;        &lt;label for=&quot;user&quot;&gt;姓名：&lt;/label&gt;        &lt;input id=&quot;user&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; placeholder=&quot;请输入用户名&quot;&gt;        &lt;label for=&quot;pass&quot;&gt;密码：&lt;/label&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;password&quot; name=&quot;pass&quot; id=&quot;pass&quot; placeholder=&quot;请输入密码&quot;&gt;        &lt;br&gt;        &lt;!-- 单选：radio --&gt;        &lt;label for=&quot;male&quot;&gt;性别：&lt;/label&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; value=&quot;male&quot; name=&quot;sex&quot; id=&quot;male&quot;&gt;男性        &lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; value=&quot;female&quot; name=&quot;sex&quot; id=&quot;female&quot;&gt;女性        &lt;br&gt;        &lt;!-- 多选:checkbox  --&gt;        &lt;label for=&quot;sports&quot;&gt;爱好：&lt;/label&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;sports&quot; name=&quot;fav&quot; id=&quot;sports&quot;&gt;运动        &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;reading&quot; name=&quot;fav&quot; id=&quot;reading&quot;&gt;读书        &lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;delicacy&quot; name=&quot;fav&quot; id=&quot;delicacy&quot;&gt;美食        &lt;br&gt;        &lt;!-- 文件 --&gt;        &lt;label for=&quot;file&quot;&gt;上传附件：&lt;/label&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;file&quot;&gt;        &lt;br&gt;        &lt;!-- 命令按钮：四种按钮：命令，提交，置位，图像按钮 --&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;命令&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;提交&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;reset&quot; value=&quot;清空&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;image&quot; src=&quot;./3rd class/img/goodbye.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;图形按钮&quot; width=&quot;2%&quot;&gt;                &lt;!-- html5 提供的新类型 --&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;email&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;url&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;color&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;date&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;time&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;datetime&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;range&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;        &lt;input type=&quot;search&quot; name=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;        &lt;!-- 多行文本框：textarea 属性：names, rows，cols,values,maxlength --&gt;        &lt;label for=&quot;selfdescr&quot;&gt;个人描述：&lt;/label&gt; &lt;br&gt;        &lt;textarea name=&quot;selfdescr&quot; id=&quot;selfdescr&quot; cols=&quot;30&quot; rows=&quot;10&quot;&gt;        &lt;/textarea&gt;        &lt;!-- 组合框：fieldset:将一组相关的输入集合在一起 --&gt;        &lt;!-- 组合框的标题：legend:组合框的标题 --&gt;        &lt;fieldset&gt;            &lt;legend&gt;健康信息：&lt;/legend&gt;            &lt;label for=&quot;name&quot;&gt;姓名：&lt;/label&gt;            &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;name&quot; id=&quot;name&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;            &lt;label for=&quot;sex&quot;&gt;性别:&lt;/label&gt;            &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;sex&quot; id=&quot;sex&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;            &lt;label for=&quot;height&quot;&gt;身高：&lt;/label&gt;            &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;height&quot; id=&quot;height&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;            &lt;label for=&quot;weight&quot;&gt;体重：&lt;/label&gt;            &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;weight&quot; id=&quot;weight&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;         &lt;/fieldset&gt;        &lt;!-- 下拉列表：select --&gt;        &lt;p&gt;下拉列表有两种形式：差别就是属性中的multiple&lt;/p&gt;        &lt;ol&gt;            &lt;li&gt;1. 单项下拉列表&lt;/li&gt;            &lt;li&gt;2. 双向下拉列表&lt;/li&gt;        &lt;/ol&gt;        &lt;h2&gt;单向下拉列表&lt;/h2&gt;        &lt;select name=&quot;fruid&quot; id=&quot;fruid&quot;&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;apple&quot;&gt;apple&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;pear&quot;&gt;pear&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;watermelon&quot;&gt;watermelon&lt;/option&gt;        &lt;/select&gt;        &lt;h2&gt;多向下拉列表&lt;/h2&gt;        &lt;select name=&quot;fav&quot; id=&quot;fav&quot; multiple=&quot;multiple&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;tr&quot;&gt;travel&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;delicacy&quot;&gt;delicacy&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;sp&quot;&gt;sports&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;music&quot;&gt;music&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;reading&quot;&gt;reading&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;option value=&quot;movie&quot;&gt;movie&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;/select&gt;        &lt;h2&gt;多向下拉分组列表&lt;/h2&gt;        &lt;select name=&quot;fav&quot; id=&quot;fav&quot; multiple=&quot;multiple&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;            &lt;optgroup label=&quot;户外运动&quot;&gt;                &lt;option value=&quot;tr&quot;&gt;travel&lt;/option&gt;                &lt;option value=&quot;sp&quot;&gt;sports&lt;/option&gt;                &lt;option value=&quot;movie&quot;&gt;movie&lt;/option&gt;                &lt;/optgroup&gt;            &lt;optgroup label=&quot;室内运动&quot;&gt;                &lt;option value=&quot;delicacy&quot;&gt;delicacy&lt;/option&gt;                &lt;option value=&quot;music&quot;&gt;music&lt;/option&gt;                &lt;option value=&quot;reading&quot;&gt;reading&lt;/option&gt;            &lt;/optgroup&gt;            &lt;/select&gt;        &lt;br&gt;                &lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;提交&quot;&gt;    &lt;/form&gt;    &lt;/body&gt;<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## 二、value、id、name详解</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- name是控件的名称 ，value是控件的值， id是控件的身份标志。</span><br><span class="line">- value：</span><br><span class="line">  - **对于 “button”、“reset”、“submit” 类型 - 定义按钮上的文本**</span><br><span class="line">  - **对于 “text”、“password”、“hidden” 类型 - 定义输入字段的初始（默认）值**</span><br><span class="line">  - **对于 “checkbox”、“radio”、“image” 类型 - 定义与 input 元素相关的值，当提交表单时该值会发送到表单的 action URL。**</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; 注意：value 属性对于 ＜input type=&quot;checkbox&quot;＞和 ＜input type=&quot;radio&quot;＞ 是必需的。</span><br><span class="line">&gt; 注意：value 属性不适用于 ＜input type=&quot;file&quot;＞</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- ＜input＞**name** 属性</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  - **name 属性规定 ＜input＞元素的名称。</span><br><span class="line">    name 属性用于在 JavaScript 中引用元素，或者在表单提交后引用表单数据。**</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &gt; 注意：只有设置了 name 属性的表单元素才能在提交表单时传递它们的值。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 总结：</span><br><span class="line">  - name主要是表单元素里才有的属性。通过js的document.表单名称.文本框.value来获取文本框的值，其中的表单名称和文本框名称指的是name,</span><br><span class="line">  - 而非表单元素例如div，span等是没有name属性的，而id属性是任何一个HTML元素都会有的。当你需要用js获取非表单元素对象是就得用document.getElementByIdx(&quot;id&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">  - value用于数据库传值，name用来标识</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## 三、地图热点</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 用坐标来选定图像的区域并关联超链接</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  ```html</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;h1&gt;地图和地图热点演示&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;img src=&quot;./img/animal.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;9 grid picture&quot; usemap=&quot;#ninegrid&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;map name=&quot;ninegrid&quot; id=&quot;ninegrid&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          &lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;0,0,120,120&quot; href=&quot;http://www.scu.edu.cn&quot; alt=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          &lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;120,0,240,120&quot; href=&quot;http://www.uestc.edu.cn&quot; alt=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          &lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;240,0,360,120&quot; href=&quot;https://www.swjtu.edu.cn/&quot; alt=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          &lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;360,0,480,120&quot; href=&quot;https://www.swufe.edu.cn/&quot; alt=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;/map&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="四、走马丁（弹幕）"><a href="#四、走马丁（弹幕）" class="headerlink" title="四、走马丁（弹幕）"></a>四、走马丁（弹幕）</h2><p>- </p>  <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>基本效果<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">behavior</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">direction</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是基础的走马灯！<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">marquee</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>behavior控制走马灯运动效果，默认循环滚动（alternate）<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">behavior</span>=<span class="string">&quot;slide&quot;</span> <span class="attr">direction</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我幻灯片模式，滚动到边停<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">marquee</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>direction 控制方向（默认left,方向从右边到左）<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">behavior</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">direction</span>=<span class="string">&quot;up&quot;</span>&gt;</span>上走马<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">marquee</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">behavior</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">direction</span>=<span class="string">&quot;down&quot;</span>&gt;</span>下走马<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">marquee</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">behavior</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">direction</span>=<span class="string">&quot;right&quot;</span>&gt;</span>右走马<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">marquee</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>scrollamout用于设置滚动速度，默认为1，值越大，速度越快，5-10适合观看<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">behavior</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">direction</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">scrollamount</span>=<span class="string">&quot;10&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是速度为5的走马灯<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">marquee</span>&gt;</span>\</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>设置滚动范围控制 width height; 滚动背景颜色 bgcolor<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">direction</span>=<span class="string">&quot;up&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100&quot;</span> <span class="attr">bgcolor</span>=<span class="string">&quot;deeppin&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>使用很简单，就是简单的属性堆叠，很多属性一查便知，在此只简单放一个实例</p></blockquote><h2 id="四、视频音频"><a href="#四、视频音频" class="headerlink" title="四、视频音频"></a>四、视频音频</h2><p>- </p>  <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>多媒体标签演示<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 音频标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">audio</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;./multimedia/mp3/bike.mp3&quot;</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>=<span class="string">&quot;controls&quot;</span> <span class="attr">autoplay</span>=<span class="string">&quot;autoplay&quot;</span> <span class="attr">loop</span>=<span class="string">&quot;loop&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       你的浏览器不支持这种音乐格式。</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">audio</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 视频标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>视频标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">video</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;./multimedia/mp4/goodbye.mp4&quot;</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>=<span class="string">&quot;controls&quot;</span> <span class="attr">autoplay</span> <span class="attr">poster</span>=<span class="string">&quot;./img/animal.jpg&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;80%&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">track</span> <span class="attr">kind</span>=<span class="string">&quot;subtitles&quot;</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;./multimedia/mp4/test.vtt&quot;</span> <span class="attr">srclang</span>=<span class="string">&quot;en&quot;</span> <span class="attr">label</span>=<span class="string">&quot;English&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       抱歉你的视频不支持嵌入字幕</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">video</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>视频播放、音频播放的使用很简单，就是简单的属性堆叠，很多属性一查便知，在此只简单放一个实例</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
